# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#  🔒 NIDS Dashboard - Environment Variables Template
#  Copy this file to .env.local and fill in your actual values
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ── 🔑 REQUIRED: API Keys ─────────────────────────────────────
# AbuseIPDB API Key (Free tier: 1,000 checks/day)
# Get from: https://www.abuseipdb.com/register
# Dashboard: https://www.abuseipdb.com/account/api
VITE_ABUSEIPDB_API_KEY=your_abuseipdb_api_key_here

# ── 🔥 REQUIRED: Firebase Configuration ──────────────────────
# Get from: https://console.firebase.google.com
# Project Settings > General > Your apps > Web app config
VITE_FIREBASE_API_KEY=your_firebase_api_key_here
VITE_FIREBASE_AUTH_DOMAIN=your-project.firebaseapp.com
VITE_FIREBASE_PROJECT_ID=your-project-id
VITE_FIREBASE_STORAGE_BUCKET=your-project.appspot.com
VITE_FIREBASE_MESSAGING_SENDER_ID=your_sender_id
VITE_FIREBASE_APP_ID=your_app_id

# ── 📝 NOTES ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 
# 🚀 VERCEL DEPLOYMENT:
# Add all VITE_* variables to your Vercel project:
# Project Settings > Environment Variables
#
# 🆓 FREE APIS USED:
# - AbuseIPDB: Threat intelligence (1,000/day free)
# - IP-API.com: Geolocation (45/min free, no key needed)
#
# ❌ REMOVED APIS:
# - IPQS (IPQualityScore): Replaced with IP-API.com
# - GreyNoise: Removed from project
#
# 🔒 SECURITY:
# Never commit .env.local to git!
# The .gitignore file protects these credentials.
#
